    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know they love me, i do. but i see the look on their faces when i ask for help. the sighs, the way they check their watches. it's like i'm just another chore on their to-do list now. i've spent my whole life looking after them, and now i'm just... i'm just a weight they have to carry. it doesn't feel right. it feels like i'm just taking up space that they could use better.",
